{"tid":1940882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【佬訊專欄】林鄭，少發高論吧！ - 佬訊","createTime":"2020-03-24T05:24:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T06:09:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7db91e6dcfbd3c2271a5808fedfeee61f66d4bb9","tid":1940882,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T05:24:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200324/WW7JBGDOMBOA6TUQXRQZQYMS5A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200324%2FWW7JBGDOMBOA6TUQXRQZQYMS5A%2F&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1sls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=34838368\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200324%2FWW7JBGDOMBOA6TUQXRQZQYMS5A%2F&h=ba886491\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200324/WW7JBGDOMBOA6TUQXRQZQYMS5A/</a><br />\n<br />\n【佬訊專欄】林鄭，少發高論吧！ - 佬訊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200324/large/1584980236_e128.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200324%2Flarge%2F1584980236_e128.jpg&h=274cabec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港政府搞一大輪都封唔到關，只能在「被封關」後才能自claim封關。林鄭，少發高論吧。 資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n「在一場惡疫的開端以及它的結尾，永遠總有一種大發高論的趨勢。在第一種情形下，那因為舊習未除；就後者而言，那是舊疾復發。只有在一場災難的中間，一個人才會鍛煉得趨向真理──換句話說，趨向沉默。」──《瘟疫》卡謬。Follow佬訊足夠耐的朋友，應該記得曾幾何時，卡謬是我們facebook cover photo的代言佬之一。喜歡他，最初是因為咬着香煙的造型太有型，後來是因為他的小說越睇越有味道。<br />\n<br />\n武肺wfh至今，卡謬的《瘟疫》佬編已經讀了兩次，上面quote的，算是印象比較深刻的一段。之所以印象深刻，除了是因為看到很多人衝出來柒之外，也是想警惕自己。作為寫文收錢的人之一，佬編自然明白大發高論的誘惑。疫情之下，題材簡直是信手拈來，like數得來而不費工夫。<br />\n<br />\n例如早前英國佛系抗疫時，便有一大班藍絲及中立人搶閘衝出來說英國是日落帝國，橫眉冷笑的模樣。殊不知兩個星期不到，英國市民被嚇到唔敢出街，留學生全數清空，醫療系統壓力大減，然後還立即有一連串配合封關封城的經濟援助措施。反觀香港政府，搞一大輪都封唔到關，只能在「被封關」後才能自claim封關，導致現在社區第二波爆發。<br />\n<br />\n在《瘟疫》的最後一章，卡謬寫道：「我們的戰略並沒有改變，但昨天顯然失敗的，今天卻似乎獲勝&hellip;&hellip;瘟疫在攻抵一切目標之後而下令收兵。」疫症是人禍，也是天災。在天災面前，人人平等，對與錯不會這麼容易有定論。在還不知道誰可以笑到最後之前，與其像林鄭認屎認屁，倒不如試吓少發高論吧。<br />\n<br />\n佬訊<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/loshunhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Floshunhk%2F&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1sls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=7b8f05e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/loshunhk/</a>"},{"pid":"c7ae0c4188062fd285b969930896df42579ac605","tid":1940882,"uid":269515,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T05:31:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j5FYgZK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj5FYgZK.png&h=10824ca3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f51f43fa069acb418a70b0f9b979be9e854e9e52","tid":1940882,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7ae0c4188062fd285b969930896df42579ac605","tid":1940882,"uid":269515,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T05:31:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j5FYgZK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj5FYgZK.png&h=10824ca3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T05:49:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4078b5bcee7aa37c8f0c4d8a1aa7eec5e66214fc","tid":1940882,"uid":83523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T06:09:11.000Z","msg":"點解佢d相張張個咀臉都咁閪"}]}